title: 60 Minute Indoor Cycling Workout | Endurance Ride
description:
Join Paul on an epic 60 minute ride, this journey will incorporate two focussed blocks of intensity and a strong finish! This longer adventure will improve your fitness, your strength and burn lot's of calories - ENJOY THE RI:ID
